Source.Name: hipblaslt
Source.Summary: hipBLASLt is a library that provides general matrix-matrix operations with a flexible API and extends functionalities beyond a traditional BLAS library
Source.Description: hipBLASLt is a library that provides general matrix-matrix operations. It has a flexible API that extends functionalities beyond a traditional BLAS library, such as adding flexibility to matrix data layouts, input types, compute types, and algorithmic implementations and heuristics.
